title: For Sale:  1/4 Time fuse AKA 'Bickford' Fuse AKA blasting fuse, AKA safety fuse.
postcontent:
1/4 fully waterproofed time fuse. This fuse will burn fully submerged with an internal burn ONLY which produces fire ONLY at the exposed ends of the fuse. You could run the middle portion of a length of this fuse through a pile of FFFFG priming powder and the powder would not ignite. Used in firework construction to pass fire through flammable/explosive material without igniting until the flame front reaches the end of the fuse. Also used in blasting etc. Uses limited only by your imagination. This is legally  the same as the common green "visco" or "cannon" fuse used in class C consumer fireworks and is not a restricted item. 

Price is 100 feet for $50.00 Comparable fuse is generally sold online for 70 cents plus per foot plus expensive shipping.

title: For Sale:  Smith & Wesson Model #1026 10MM *RARE*
postcontent:
Only 3,135 made. Smith and Wesson-Model 1026-10mm-semi-auto pistol with 5-inch barrel and (2) 9-round magazines. This is a limited production model with only 3,135 manufactured. Originally requested by the FBI for more stopping power than the 9mm or 45acp. This model allows firing of a round with the magazine removed. It features a separate side lever de-cocker. The only other Smith & Wesson 10mm that was designed this way was the Model 1076 which has a 4 inch barrel and 13,805 of those were manufactured, making the 1026 over four times more rare. 

Includes (2) 9-round magazines, case and factory cleaning kit.

Will sell to current CFP holders only - no exceptions! Local, CASH sales only, please.
